Package: kochab-agent
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Kochab <hello@kochab.ai>
Depends: systemd
Description: Kochab infrastructure monitoring agent
 Lightweight agent that connects a Linux server to the Kochab platform
 over an HTTPS long-polling control channel. Reports task results,
 buffers payloads when offline, and integrates with systemd watchdog.
